text: "500 Keys" is the 21st episode of the 22nd season of The Simpsons. It was first shown on the Fox network on May 15, 2011. It was written by John Frink. Bob Anderson is the director of the episode. The episode is about the Simpson family finding many different keys. == References == Category:2011 television episodes Category:The Simpsons episodes
